text: "I d-d-don't sup-p-p-pose you here to kill that rich BASTARD, are ya?"
"Regadless of t-t-that, the DEVs are lazy A-A-A-holes, so this dungeon is incomplete!"
"Are you trying to kill--- THAT R-RICH SUCKER!??"
"Hmm you know w-w-what? I wanna join too, B-B-BUT I DON'T KNOW THE CODE"
"H-h-he's right there, with his M-M-MASIVE pile of money!"
"O-o-okay... We should have gathered enought i-i-information..."
"An i-i-inverstment of 3 MILLIONS on the FIRST MONTH."
"He t-t-then he spent those 3 MILLIONS on the SECOND MONTH."
"A-a-and then lost other 2 MILLIONS on the THIRD MONTH."
"Lastly he m-m-managed to get 9 MILLIONS back. TCH."
"B-b-but first take this with you. I-i-it's too dangerous to go a-a-alone."
"On the F-F-FIRST MONTH he got an inversment of 3 MILLIONS!?"
"I-i-it seems that on the S-S-SECOND MONTH he spent 3 MILLIONS!"
"C-c-can't you see I'm b-b-busy?? D-d-do your part of the work!"
"On the T-T-THIRD MONTH he lost 2 MILLIONS!!"
"NOOOO h-h-he got back 9 M-M-MILLIONS on the FOURTH MONTH!!"
"Such a shame... I actually missed you, you know..."
"Now all you want is REVENGE... PATHETIC HELL-STRAY CAT"
"Si te gustan los gatitos y ruptura de la cuarta pared."
"Si te gustan los isekai y humor negro."
